OL,3,CPottery firm saved from liquidation
OL,4,Cafter founder's grandson buys company
OL,6,FMoorcroft Pottery in Stoke on Trent
OL,7,Fhas been saved from liquidation after
OL,8,Fthe grandson of the company's founder
OL,9,FWilliam Moorcroft bought it.
OL,11,F57 workers lost their jobs when the
OL,12,Fcompany went bust earlier this year.
OL,14,FBut now Will Moorcroft has secured the
OL,15,Fcompany along with its assets and
OL,16,Fbrought it back into family ownership
OL,17,Ffor the first time in nearly 20 years.
