OL,3,CPottery firm saved from liquidation
OL,4,Cafter founder's grandson buys company
OL,6,FSpeaking about the news, the new
OL,7,Fowner, Mr Moorcroft he said: "The
OL,8,Freturn of Moorcroft is wonderful not
OL,9,Fjust for the ceramics industry, but
OL,10,Ffor the City of Stoke-on-Trent as it
OL,11,Fcelebrates it's centenary year, and in
OL,12,Fparticular the talented staff, many of
OL,13,Fwho have been with the firm for their
OL,14,Fentire working lives.
OL,16,FHe added: "This is a moment for them
OL,17,Fto celebrate because Moorcroft is so
OL,18,Fmuch more than a job.
